<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Your Trial Has Ended</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body>
  {{> header}}

  <div style="padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;">
    <h1 style="color: #dc3545;">Your Trial Has Ended</h1>

    <p>Hi {{customerName}},</p>

    <p>Your free trial for <strong>{{companyName}}</strong> ended on <strong>{{trialEndDate}}</strong>.</p>

    <p>Your account access is now limited, but you can subscribe at any time to restore full access and continue using all features.</p>

    <div style="background: #f8d7da; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;">
      <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Important: Your data will be removed on {{dataRemovalDate}}</strong></p>
      <ul style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li>All your photographs, albums, and settings will be permanently deleted</li>
        <li>Client galleries and contact sheets will no longer be accessible</li>
        <li>This action cannot be undone after the removal date</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #d4edda; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #28a745;">
      <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Subscribe now to keep your data</strong></p>
      <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">Upgrade to a paid plan before {{dataRemovalDate}} to retain all your work and continue using the platform.</p>
    </div>

    {{#if upgradeUrl}}
    <p style="margin: 30px 0; text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{upgradeUrl}}" style="background: #28a745; color: white; padding: 14px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">
        Subscribe Now
      </a>
    </p>
    {{/if}}

    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
      We hope to see you back soon!
    </p>

    <p style="color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 40px;">
      If you have any questions about our plans or need assistance, please contact our support team.
    </p>
  </div>

  {{> footer}}
</body>
</html>
